00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:14,170
”Three Lives, Three Worlds” by Jason Zhang

2
00:00:14,170 --> 00:00:17,630
♫ Listen to the rustling of the wind ♫

3
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:21,210
